| 
| Abstract concept of a proxy description of a party, including an optional link to data for
| this party in a demographic or other identity management system. Sub- typed into
| `PARTY_IDENTIFIED` and `PARTY_SELF`.
| 

abstract class PARTY_PROXY
    is_a Any

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Optional reference to more detailed demographic or identification information for this
    | party, in an external system.
    | 
    prop external_ref: PARTY_REF;


end
